commit.message:
fix: customers page - response formats, pagination, search, missing endpoints

Worker changes:
- /customers: add pagination (page/pageSize), search, return { customers, total, totalPages }
- /customers/:id DELETE: cascade delete reservations + work orders
- /customers/batch-fix-age POST: set child_age_years=0 where only months set
- /menu-items: wrap response as { menu_items }
- /locations: wrap response as { locations }
- /users: wrap response as { users }
- /reservations: add customer_ids filter, return { reservations }
- /work-orders: add reservation_ids filter, return { work_orders }
- /work-orders/reorder POST: save priority_order for multiple items
- /reservations/batch-create-work-orders POST: auto-create work orders
- /calendar-data + /calendar/bulk: also return locations, menu_items, users, work_orders

DB changes:
- getCustomers: paginated with search support
- getReservationsByCustomerIds: new function
- getWorkOrdersByReservationIds: new function
- upsertCustomer: add external_customer_number, child_age_years, child_age_months
- upsertWorkOrder: add all columns (delivered_date, pickup_date, priority_order, etc.)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
